SQLite-VirtualTable
===================

This module allows to create SQLite Virtual Table extensions in Perl.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL SQLITE_SOURCE=/path/to/sqlite/source
   make
   make test
   make install

and to make the extension available to any SQLite application:

   cp blib/lib/auto/SQLite/VirtualTable/perlvtab.so /usr/local/lib/

or add to LD_LIBRARY_PATH the directory where it is installed.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Test::More
   Text::CSV_XS in order to use the sample CSV driver.

